title: 'Gas Hat' Jan. 6 rioter who first breached Capitol tunnel entrance arrested by FBI
description: The man who federal authorities say set off a brutal battle with police at the lower west tunnel of the U.S. Capitol on Jan. 6 was arrested Friday.

title: Mila Kunis, Ashton Kutcher say they're 'aware of the pain' their Danny Masterson defense letters caused
description: Mila Kunis and Ashton Kutcher said they are "aware of the pain" their character letters defending convicted rapist Danny Masterson caused, stating their intent was not to re-traumatize the victims or undermine the verdict.

title: NFL 'Sunday Ticket' expected to have major delays on YouTube TV
description: As the NFL's "Sunday Ticket" returns for another season, experts warn not to be surprised if major delays occur with the switch to YouTube TV’s streaming service.

title: Rescue begins for American scientist trapped 3,000 feet inside Turkish cave
description: Rescuers have begun to free an American scientist who became stranded deep inside a cave in Turkey after he fell ill.

title: With Xi and Putin absent, Biden steps into the power void to woo allies at G20
description: If showing up is one of life’s basic tenets, President Joe Biden may have one-upped his rivals the moment he stepped off Air Force One and set foot on Indian soil.

title: Prominent activist’s son convicted of storming Capitol and invading Senate floor in Jan. 6 riot
description: The son of a prominent conservative activist has been convicted of charges that he stormed the U.S.

title: Escaped Pennsylvania killer spotted twice on same day as search zone narrows in on fugitive
description: Escaped prisoner Danelo Cavalcante was spotted twice on Friday within the Chester County search area, Pennsylvania state police said, as officials appear to narrow in on the fugitive by reducing the search zone.

title: Alabama cracks down on birth centers, leaving pregnant women with fewer options
description: Doctors and midwives in Alabama say birth centers could help tackle its dangerously high maternal mortality rate. They're fighting the state to open.

title: 'The whole thing's a mess': Anger and panic as ADHD drug shortages drag on
description: The U.S. has been stuck in a shortage for Adderall and other ADHD medications for nearly a year. Experts doubt the situation will improve soon.

title: Coco Gauff set to be latest Black American woman to make her mark at U.S. Open
description: Coco Gauff hopes to be the latest Black American woman to leave a history-making mark on the most sacred grounds of U.S. tennis.

title: Darfur refugees recount ethnic violence as Sudan’s civil war reignites genocide fears
description: As Darfur refugees recount horrors witnessed while fleeing to safety, the U.S.'s U.N. ambassador warns Sudan's genocide may be starting again.

title: 6.8-magnitude earthquake strikes Morocco, damaging buildings and sending people into the streets
description: A powerful earthquake struck Morocco late Friday, damaging buildings in major cities and sending panicked people pouring into streets and alleyways from the capital Rabat to Marrakech, the county’s most visited tourist destination.
